      "sourceUrlId": "https://www.wtr-lab.com/id/novel/59412/i-started-with-a-natural-disaster-so-i-stockpiled-billions-of-resources-and-then-just-sat-around-doing-nothing-in-the-apocalypse",
      "titleEn": "Doulou Continent: Blue Overlord",
      "titleId": "Doulou Continent: Blue Overlord",
      "author": "Qu You Le Chang",
      "descriptionEn": "While watching the Douluo Continent anime, Yu Tiancheng was unexpectedly struck by lightning and transmigrated, becoming a direct disciple of the Blue Lightning Tyrant Dragon Clan! Knowing the original story intimately, he was acutely aware that his clan was about to be massacred by the Spirit Hall! To rewrite his clan's fate, he decided to intercept Tang San and seize all his opportunities! Immortal herbs, spirit rings, divine inheritance… he would grab them all! Fortunately, although he lacked a system, he possessed the heaven-defying ability to devour lightning! He tempered his body with lightning, causing his spirit power to surge! He forged an invincible path with lightning, vowing to ascend to godhood and suppress all enemies!",
